          <div style={{background:BG_SUBTLE,borderRadius:12,padding:18,marginBottom:24,border:`1px solid ${BORDER}`}}><div style={{fontFamily:heading,fontWeight:700,fontSize:14,marginBottom:6}}>A note on these estimates</div><div style={{fontSize:13,color:TEXT_MED,lineHeight:1.7}}>Premiums are estimates. Actual plans and subsidies vary by ZIP. Our advisors do exact comparisons for free.</div></div>
